{"tid":2398223,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE多賢&彩瑛神還原熱門曲《換成我吧》預告公開，粉絲：她們越認真我越想笑XD","createTime":"2021-02-07T06:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T08:11:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef3f65a37f57b8293a6bae8f3a7cdbf285713000","tid":2398223,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_3b418b4599a95d7cba1442906ae21d53/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-07/133548-896275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_3b418b4599a95d7cba1442906ae21d53%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-07%2F133548-896275.jpg&h=f3c4ee35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比起 cover 舞蹈，小編更期待這部 MV 的劇情啊～！XDDD 原曲：RAIN&amp;JYP《Switch to me》<br />\n<br />\n人氣女團 TWICE 中的經典雙人組又來啦！成員多賢和彩瑛每一次推出模仿都能製造笑料，從「幼稚園角色」到「太陽的後裔」都令粉絲印象深刻，這一次則是挑戰RAIN&amp;JYP的熱門新歌《換成我吧》（Switch to me），預告一出便引發熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_7ec33ea18f7ad8affc0e8162802abd0d/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-07/133548-896280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_7ec33ea18f7ad8affc0e8162802abd0d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-07%2F133548-896280.png&h=8cde5609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖源：twicetagram@IG）<br />\n<br />\n▼預告全新音樂企劃，由多賢和彩瑛主演的《換成我吧》，兩人完美復刻原版MV開場，嚴肅地討論著身高的話題，手中的酒還換成了牛奶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_OCrLKPweys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_OCrLKPweys&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=a2f0a82e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_OCrLKPweys</a><br />\n<br />\n彩瑛：「歐逆（姐）最近很開心吧！長高了1公分。」<br />\n多賢：「我還是老樣子啦！倒是妳&hellip;最近也長高了0.7公分，很出名嘛～。」<br />\n彩瑛：「可是要追上歐逆還差地遠呢。」<br />\n多賢：「我看快了，因為你能做到不擇手段嘛。」<br />\n彩瑛：「那也都是跟歐逆學到的啊。」<br />\n眼神對峙～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c4255c00771204460a4ec39560cfbed7/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-07/133548-896279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c4255c00771204460a4ec39560cfbed7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-07%2F133548-896279.jpg&h=71143892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼原版MV：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Bf_BB9iTNI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-Bf_BB9iTNI&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=0170ec10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Bf_BB9iTNI</a><br />\n<br />\n不曉得這個音樂企劃，會不會有女主角呢？因為是身高的話題，會是隊內最高的子瑜登場嗎？<br />\n<br />\n多賢和彩瑛版的《換成我吧》音樂企劃，將會在2月10日的晚間六點完整公開，真的好期待啊～！<br />\n<br />\n（封面&amp;內文圖源：RAIN's Official Channel@youtube.com／TWICE @youtube.com）"},{"pid":"fffc979811e81f89f24ce95b3947fa67a36fd8a4","tid":2398223,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:13:29.000Z","msg":"好想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf66dfe0ced0ef5c2fc7bcf7d0edc7f5d27f279","tid":2398223,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fffc979811e81f89f24ce95b3947fa67a36fd8a4","tid":2398223,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:13:29.000Z","msg":"好想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:14:52.000Z","msg":"唔好搞咁多野喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cadb2d49eef905998b4087b53c1b13b7b35efe","tid":2398223,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"掂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9229a57c74f3612a6b4169c47aa44a672f781c","tid":2398223,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87cadb2d49eef905998b4087b53c1b13b7b35efe","tid":2398223,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"掂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"太勁了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895332c41572e2fa5d1ccada356f55190c75235f","tid":2398223,"uid":274500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"多腎solo?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}